data.description: Welcome to this magnificent custom built very spacious retreat! Perfect for multiple residents or a vacation get away. Granite countertops, wood flooring and tilework throughout a majority of this 6-bedroom, multiple bonus rooms and 4 1/2 bathroom home. There is a front porch and rebuilt full length back deck which leads to the luxurious built in resurfaced swimming pool.  There are many balconies perfect for an herb garden and stargazing. With full solar, whole house generator, central heat/air along with an evaporative cooler,  ceiling fans and a new cozy wood burning stove   you are sure to be comfortable while minimizing out of pocket expenses. 24ft deep garage with basement area behind offers ample storage for your goodies. Animal stables and tack room as well as multiple animal enclosures and a small year-round duck pond for your furry friends. The property is fully fenced, gated and cross fenced at the rear of the home as well as in the dog run area. There are several types of fruit bearing trees including cherry, apple, apricot, citrus, fig, nectarine and peach. Along with that there are a variety of berry bushes. This is a beautifully unique set up with many upgrades, fantastic views and placed upon two acres of level land. Priced to move! 2023-12-19
